00:49:52.510 --> 00:49:54.349
There are two kinds of
orangutan males.

00:49:54.349 --> 00:49:56.989
There's a large one and a small
one.

00:49:56.989 --> 00:50:01.219
The big males are about 200
pounds, the females and the

00:50:01.219 --> 00:50:05.920
