further.

00:50:14.110 --> 00:50:17.889
Doesn't develop the
characteristics of the full

00:50:17.889 --> 00:50:21.668
male, doesn't grow a beard,
crests of the hair,

00:50:21.668 --> 00:50:23.639
throat pouches,
etc.

00:50:23.639 --> 00:50:26.320
